  "description": "A wide-angle view showcases a layered landscape of rolling hills and distant mountains under a dramatic sky filled with puffy white clouds. The foreground is dominated by lush green trees with varying shades of foliage, partially obscuring glimpses of residential buildings nestled amongst them. The hills transition into darker, shadowed ranges further back, culminating in the hazy blue of the distant mountains. The clouds are bright white and cast soft shadows on the landscape. The overall composition evokes a sense of depth and natural beauty.",
